{"title":"与农工党同志共勉","authors":["周谷城"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"与农工党同志共勉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周谷城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）振奋精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相监督共长存，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字珠玑作指针。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一事吾侪须记取，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神气魄要全新。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）学习理论"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"启聋振聩有前知，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列毛书未过时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"识得必然方自在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从知潜力涌于斯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）加强组织"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创始经营六十春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今参政更分明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前辈功劳虽可贵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加强组织靠同人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）努力四化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四化宏图事不凡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要同领导向前看。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农工医卫加科技，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一篑功成九仞山。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}